text: Lina Rohe is a German water polo player. She was part of the Germany women's national water polo team at the 2003 World Aquatics Championships, 2006 Women's European Water Polo Championship, and 2007 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * FINA world championship day 13, zimbio * FINA world championship day 0 zimbio * lina-rohe-of-germany- looks-to-pass category:German water polo players Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
